		</section>

		<Section title='About'>
			<p class='text-muted-foreground'>
                Hello! I'm Animesh, a <b>Full Stack Software Engineer</b> based in India.
                I enjoy creating things that live on the internet, whether that be websites, applications, or anything in between.
                Currently I'm building <b>Vanijya - AI Agent Workforce for SMEs and Social Commerce</b>.
			</p>
		</Section>
		{
			allPostsByDate.length > 0 && (
				<Section title='Posts'>
					<ul class='flex flex-col gap-y-2'>
						{allPostsByDate.map((p) => (
							<li class='flex flex-col gap-x-2 sm:flex-row'>
								<PostPreview post={p} />
							</li>
						))}
					</ul>
				</Section>
			)
		}

		<Section title='Experience'>
			<Card
				heading='Senior Software Engineer'
				subheading='Tata 1MG'
				date='April 2024 - Present'
				imagePath='/src/assets/about-astro.png'
				altText='Senior Software Engineer for Tata 1MG'
				imageClass='h-12 w-auto md:-left-16'
			>
				<ul class='ml-4 list-disc text-muted-foreground'>
                    <li>
                        Working on B2B Order Management System for 1MG's Pharmacy and Diagnostics services.
					</li>
                    <li>
                        Core Contributor on Common Order Taking (COT) Engine that creates a unified order taking system undetaking POS, Telesales, Third Party and All Other Order Channels.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                    Build OneDoc - A Confluence Alternative with AI Capabilities for Storing Tech Documents, PRDs and Chatting with Internal Data.
                    </li>
