				imagePath='/src/assets/about-astro.png'
				altText='Senior Software Engineer for Meetri'
				imageClass='h-12 w-auto md:-left-16'
			>
				<ul class='ml-4 list-disc text-muted-foreground'>
                    <li>
                        Led Merchant Integration Team at Meetri, built scalable order management systems with AWS/Kafka (500k+ MAUs), developed Multi-Tenant services, and created an API Gateway with RBAC and advanced features.
					</li>
