				imagePath='/src/assets/about-astro.png'
				altText='Software Consultant for Ministry of Education'
				imageClass='h-12 w-auto md:-left-16'
			>
            <ul class='ml-4 list-disc text-muted-foreground'>
                <li>
                    Designed and Launched a <b>Multi-Tenant monolithic Innovation Management Tool</b> to be used by 30+ educational institutions from
                </li>
            </ul>
            </Card>
			<Card
				heading='Software Engineer'
				subheading='Rishikul Herbal'
				date='Jab 2021 - Oct 2021'
				imagePath='/src/assets/about-astro.png'
				altText='Software Consultant'
				imageClass='h-12 w-auto md:-left-16'
			>
            <ul class='ml-4 list-disc text-muted-foreground'>
                <li>
                    Build the Entire Order Taking Website from scratch using React and NodeJS. Hosted on AWS Stack and Scaled to 10k Daily users.
                </li>
            </ul>
